name: MIA 001
description:
Poetry is a new venture but I seem to have a back log of words ready to come forth. Readings of this first piece have gone down very well and now is your chance to own a copy and savour it yourself.

My first poetry zine featuring two poems across seven double sided pages. Printed in black and white. Signed and numbered in a limited edition of 100.

Selling out quick and featuring poetry performed at Kats and Dogs open mic, Queer Zine Festival (2012), Wotever World at the Royal Vauxhall Tavern and DIY Cultures (2013) at Rich Mix

name: MIA 002
description: The second zine featuring my writing is in production and will be printed in a limited edition of 100 like the first. Stay tuned for more details

name: Online Tarot Reading
description:
I seem to have quite an affinity with the cards and with many happy customers. For £8 you get a three card tarot spread channelled with your spirits. I will email you the results.

Please also keep in mind that I usually have my cards at events so you can just come and offer to cross my palm with silver!!!

name: Donations for Materials and Tools
description:
Help inspire me and expand my portfolio by donating just £4.20 for art materials and tools. I don't make a living from my art but I would like to and maybe you can help!

Please donate today safe in the knowledge that I will funnelling it back into the arts and fuelling my creativity. I can't keep on creating new work without some funding so please get involved. Thank you!!!
